Callicles’ position has been made much more difficolt hythe proposal for his ward's hand, and the question how to provide a dowry for her without revealing the existence of the treasure— first complication. To obviate this difficulty a Sycophant is hired to say that he comes from Charmides with letters and money. But Charmides returns unexpectedly at this moment, and encounters the Sycophant‚ who does not know him, outside his own house, when aludicrous scene takes place.
